*Smešila* se svim šalama (She laughed at all the jokes).

*Smejala* se bez zastoja (She was laughing non-stop).

*Smelo* je ustao i počeo da se obraća prisutnima (He bravely stood up and started addressing the audience).

*Smestio* se u fotelju (He settled into the armchair).

*Smem* da ti pokažem svoj dar (I dare to show you my gift).

*Smestila* se u malu sobu (She moved into the small room).